  </section>

  <!-- ============================ FAQ ============================ -->
  <section class="faq" id="faq">
    <div class="wrap faq-inner">

      <div class="faq-head">
        <span class="kicker">Frequently asked · plainly answered</span>
        <div class="title">Reasonable <em>questions</em>.</div>
        <p class="note">A roof is the second-biggest purchase most homeowners make. We figured you'd want clear answers.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="faq-list" id="faqList">

        <div class="qa open">
          <button class="qa-q"><span>Is it really free? What's the catch?</span><span class="plus"></span></button>
          <div class="qa-a"><p>Yes, free. No trial, no paywall, no email gate. We make money from optional referrals to local contractors once you've picked a color — and only if you ask for one. The tool itself is and will stay free.</p></div>
        </div>

        <div class="qa">
          <button class="qa-q"><span>Do I need to sign up or create an account?</span><span class="plus"></span></button>
          <div class="qa-a"><p>No. Upload, visualize, save, share. We don't even ask for an email. If you want to save a gallery you can — but it's opt-in, not required.</p></div>
        </div>

        <div class="qa">
          <button class="qa-q"><span>How accurate is the AI mask?</span><span class="plus"></span></button>
          <div class="qa-a"><p>On typical daylight front-of-house photos, the mask hits about 99% on flat planes and 95%+ around fiddly bits like chimneys, vents, and skylights. If something looks off you can nudge the edges by hand in two taps.</p></div>
        </div>

        <div class="qa">
          <button class="qa-q"><span>Which brands and SKUs are covered?</span><span class="plus"></span></button>
          <div class="qa-a"><p>GAF, Owens Corning, CertainTeed, IKO, Malarkey, Atlas, and TAMKO — 184 SKUs across architectural, designer, and luxury lines. We refresh the library weekly as manufacturers add or retire colors.</p></div>
        </div>

        <div class="qa">
          <button class="qa-q"><span>Does it work on my phone?</span><span class="plus"></span></button>
          <div class="qa-a"><p>That's where most people use it. The whole experience is built mobile-first — upload from your camera roll, swap colors with your thumb, save the render to your photos.</p></div>
        </div>

        <div class="qa">
          <button class="qa-q"><span>Are you affiliated with any manufacturer?</span><span class="plus"></span></button>
          <div class="qa-a"><p>No. We're independent. The brand order on this page is arbitrary, the rendering quality is the same for all of them, and we don't accept payment to push one over another.</p></div>
        </div>

        <div class="qa">
          <button class="qa-q"><span>Will my photo be used to train your model?</span><span class="plus"></span></button>
          <div class="qa-a"><p>Not unless you explicitly opt in. By default your upload is processed, returned to you, and deleted from our servers within 24 hours.</p></div>
        </div>

